name: 李·马歇尔
introduction: Lee Marshall is a Canadian actor/producer who grew up in the Philippines .She stars in the upcoming psychological thriller Bleed With Me (2020), award-winning body horror short Undress Me (2017) and twisted sci-fi short Upload:U (2017). On television, she appeared in the Emmy-award-winning crime drama "19-2" (CTV) and the true crime series "The Detectives" (CBC). In 2019, she finally shot something her relatives can watch without covering their eyes in fear: a family-friendly romcom starring Olivia Holt and Cheryl Hines called Turkey Drop (Freeform).
